<!--
    UNIVERSAL MODIFICATION COMPONENTS

    These components enable fire mode modifications across multiple weapons.
    A single inventory item can be attached to any compatible weapon in its category.

    COMPONENT_GLOCK_SWITCH - Universal Glock auto sear (works on all 9mm/10mm Glocks)
    COMPONENT_AR15_BUMPSTOCK - Universal bump stock (works on all AR-15 platform rifles)
    COMPONENT_SMG_SWITCH - Universal SMG conversion (works on compatible SMGs)
-->

